io.craigmiller160.school.entity

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.craigmiller160.school.entity.Course
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Course>

    @Entity
public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Course>, java.io.Serializable
    An entity that defines a course that students can take. It contains the attributes defining the course, and a list of all students currently taking it.

    THREAD SAFETY: This class is NOT thread-safe. Its state is not synchronized, and instances of it should be handled in a way that is not shared between threads.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    craig
